1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:05,000
[SPEAKER_00] Drage naše osnažene, dobrodošle u novu epizodu našeg podcasta.

2
00:00:05,000 --> 00:00:12,000
[SPEAKER_00] S moje desne strane, jedna prekrasna mlada dama, prekrasna žena, majka kraljica.

3
00:00:12,000 --> 00:00:15,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ona mlada.

4
00:00:15,000 --> 00:00:26,000
