9
00:00:47,000 --> 00:00:50,000
[SPEAKER_01] Oj, oj, to nisam odavno.

10
00:00:50,000 --> 00:00:54,000
[SPEAKER_01] Pa ništa, evo, ja sam Pamela Ramljak, neću već koliko imam godina.

11
00:00:54,000 --> 00:00:56,000
[SPEAKER_01] Googlajte.

12
00:00:56,000 --> 00:01:03,000
