309
00:20:13,900 --> 00:20:16,039
[SPEAKER_01] kad ima puno snimanja, druženja i tako.

310
00:20:16,039 --> 00:20:18,859
[SPEAKER_01] I uvijek nam je lijepo zajedno, evo, fakat nam je lijepo.

311
00:20:18,859 --> 00:20:22,720
[SPEAKER_00] Znači, onda se ti procvjetila 2022. godine kad ste se ponovo, ono, okupili.

312
00:20:22,720 --> 00:20:25,720
[SPEAKER_01] A mi smo već pričali o tome i godinama prije, znaš, kao očimo.

313
00:20:25,720 --> 00:20:28,079
[SPEAKER_01] Nećemo nikaj bila u Rusiji, pa ono, uvijek je bilo nešto,

314
00:20:28,079 --> 00:20:30,319
[SPEAKER_01] kao pa jedna trpa sam ja, bila trudna s Marijom,

315
00:20:30,319 --> 00:20:33,059
[SPEAKER_01] uvijek je bilo nešto, jedna smo kao tad rekli,

316
00:20:33,059 --> 00:20:36,660
[SPEAKER_01] e, ajmo sad, ajmo sad, a bile smo u kontaktu, znaš, tako da, evo.

317
00:20:36,660 --> 00:20:41,920
[SPEAKER_00] A ovaj, je li, sad kad gledaš na neku solo karijeru

318
00:20:41,920 --> 00:20:48,339
[SPEAKER_00] i gledaš skupno vas tri, je li možda lakše biti solo

319
00:20:48,339 --> 00:20:52,539
[SPEAKER_00] u smislu zbog odnosa, ali opet s druge strane je,

320
00:20:52,720 --> 00:20:55,619
[SPEAKER_00] kad se i nešto negativno događa i maš ekipu

321
00:20:55,619 --> 00:20:58,960
[SPEAKER_00] koja ti čuva leđa, ali opet s druge strane vjerujem

322
00:20:58,960 --> 00:21:02,299
[SPEAKER_00] i da solo dio, kad si sama, ima isto neke prednosti.

323
00:21:02,299 --> 00:21:06,339
[SPEAKER_01] Kako ne, mislim, ja sam jako ponosna na taj svoj album

324
00:21:06,339 --> 00:21:09,339
[SPEAKER_01] i ne znam, snimila sam i duet sa Dženan Olončarevićem,

325
00:21:09,339 --> 00:21:12,359
[SPEAKER_01] to je moja autorska pjesma i tekst i glazba

326
00:21:12,359 --> 00:21:14,980
[SPEAKER_01] i cijeli taj moj album je moj tekst i glazba

327
00:21:14,980 --> 00:21:17,900
[SPEAKER_01] i to je nešto što sam ja morala ispoljiti iz sebe

328
00:21:17,900 --> 00:21:21,480
[SPEAKER_01] te neke pjesme i čak sam snimila jednu tu

329
00:21:21,480 --> 00:21:24,420
[SPEAKER_01] slavonsku pjesmu za mamu, jer mama jako voli tamburice.

330
00:21:24,420 --> 00:21:28,960
[SPEAKER_01] I evo, ispoljili smo joj želju zadnjih,

331
00:21:28,960 --> 00:21:31,880
[SPEAKER_01] 15 godina mi govori kako bih voljela da imamo konje u spotu

332
00:21:31,880 --> 00:21:33,960
[SPEAKER_01] i sad imamo u zadnjim spotu, family, konje,

333
00:21:33,960 --> 00:21:35,920
[SPEAKER_01] znači ispoljila sam joj sve želje.

334
00:21:35,920 --> 00:21:40,640
[SPEAKER_01] I nešto, uživala sam ja u tom svom projektu.

335
00:21:40,640 --> 00:21:42,980
[SPEAKER_01] Znači, to je meni bilo lijepo.

336
00:21:42,980 --> 00:21:45,960
[SPEAKER_01] I istok se rodila i moj band,

337
00:21:45,960 --> 00:21:48,619
[SPEAKER_01] koji me trenutno prati i sa mojim prijateljem,

338
00:21:48,740 --> 00:21:51,480
[SPEAKER_01] Maksom Hozićom, znači ja radim evente, vjenčanja,

339
00:21:51,480 --> 00:21:53,859
[SPEAKER_01] svašta već, evo, 11 godina.

340
00:21:53,859 --> 00:21:57,859
[SPEAKER_01] I to je stvarno ono nešto što volim i što mi ispunjava.

341
00:21:57,859 --> 00:22:02,599
[SPEAKER_01] Tako da meni je dobro, samo dobro donijela ta solo karijera.

342
00:22:03,359 --> 00:22:10,259
[SPEAKER_01] A i nekako sam tu, ono, znaš, vidjela da volim biti u kolektivu, znaš.

343
00:22:10,259 --> 00:22:12,339
[SPEAKER_01] I jedno ne isključuje drugo.

344
00:22:12,339 --> 00:22:16,960
[SPEAKER_01] Znači, meni niko ne branje da ja i dan danas bi mogla snimiti opet nešto za sebe,

345
00:22:16,960 --> 00:22:20,720
[SPEAKER_01] ali smo opet zajedno, isto ko što i Neda i Nika,

346
00:22:20,720 --> 00:22:22,920
[SPEAKER_01] one isto, znaš, imaju te neke solo projekte,

347
00:22:22,920 --> 00:22:26,920
[SPEAKER_01] Neda još ima i Galato sestre i radi sa svojim bratom i sestrom,

348
00:22:27,019 --> 00:22:28,880
[SPEAKER_01] parmači, triodzeći, ne daj na sto strana.

349
00:22:28,880 --> 00:22:32,940
[SPEAKER_01] Tako da, ovaj, sve je to glazba, znaš, sve je to glazba

350
00:22:32,940 --> 00:22:36,700
[SPEAKER_01] i sve se to može usporedo hendlati, pogotovo u Hrvatskoj.

351
00:22:36,700 --> 00:22:39,440
[SPEAKER_01] Mislim da se ne leže, u nas je četiri miliona nešti, ono, znaš,

352
00:22:39,440 --> 00:22:42,039
[SPEAKER_01] to je posao oko bilo koji drugi.

353
00:22:42,039 --> 00:22:45,180
[SPEAKER_01] Znaš, evo, eventualno tu nas i neko vidi na televiziji,

354
00:22:45,180 --> 00:22:47,779
[SPEAKER_01] ali nije to, znaš, nije to neki glamur ili nešto.

355
00:22:47,779 --> 00:22:51,400
[SPEAKER_01] Znaš, idem doma, čistim, kuham, kod sletka druga žena,

356
00:22:51,400 --> 00:22:54,940
[SPEAKER_01] znaš, ono, apsolutno ništa posebno,

357
00:22:55,359 --> 00:22:58,420
[SPEAKER_01] samo što, eto, si kao prepoznatljiv nekome na cesti.

358
00:22:58,420 --> 00:23:01,140
[SPEAKER_00] Sada si spomenula čišćenje i kuhanje,

359
00:23:01,140 --> 00:23:05,019
[SPEAKER_00] pa kako izgleda onda to sve uz majčinstvo,

360
00:23:05,019 --> 00:23:09,619
[SPEAKER_00] uz dvoje djece i sve ono što djeca samo po sebi nose,

361
00:23:09,619 --> 00:23:12,720
[SPEAKER_00] uz odgoj, kako izgleda neka vaša svakodnevica?

362
00:23:12,720 --> 00:23:14,799
[SPEAKER_01] O, pa ja ti još čistim i apartman,

363
00:23:14,799 --> 00:23:16,500
[SPEAKER_01] ja sam ti još profesionalni čistač.

364
00:23:16,500 --> 00:23:18,279
[SPEAKER_01] Znaš, šta čim za sebeš?

365
00:23:18,279 --> 00:23:20,700
[SPEAKER_01] Pa znate, ja sam profesor glazbe, pjevačica,

366
00:23:20,700 --> 00:23:23,920
[SPEAKER_01] imam apartman, čistačica sam i vodim goste.

367
00:23:24,700 --> 00:23:26,720
[SPEAKER_01] Znaš, meni ti to ništa, ono, neki me ljudi pita,

368
00:23:26,720 --> 00:23:28,240
[SPEAKER_01] pa ti sama čistiš ta apartman,

369
00:23:28,240 --> 00:23:30,880
[SPEAKER_01] kako ti se da, kako mi sve ne bi dalo,

370
00:23:30,880 --> 00:23:32,779
[SPEAKER_01] znaš, ono, to mi je kruh za obitelj

371
00:23:32,779 --> 00:23:34,720
[SPEAKER_01] i zašto ne?

372
00:23:34,720 --> 00:23:36,640
[SPEAKER_01] Ja sam prilično ovako,

373
00:23:36,640 --> 00:23:38,339
[SPEAKER_01] kome god zna i ko je bio kod mene doma,

374
00:23:38,339 --> 00:23:39,480
[SPEAKER_01] ja sam jako pedantna,

375
00:23:39,480 --> 00:23:41,799
[SPEAKER_01] to je nešto ono kao što mogu kontrolirati,

376
00:23:41,799 --> 00:23:43,380
[SPEAKER_01] pizna su mi to ono za ostaci

377
00:23:43,380 --> 00:23:45,160
[SPEAKER_01] iz 20. do nas i odnosi, znaš.

378
00:23:45,160 --> 00:23:47,299
[SPEAKER_01] I onda je to jedino nešto što mogu kontrolirati,

379
00:23:47,299 --> 00:23:48,640
[SPEAKER_01] ovo je drugo sve u Božim rukama,

380
00:23:49,000 --> 00:23:51,519
[SPEAKER_01] ali čistoću svog stana mogu kontrolirati

381
00:23:51,519 --> 00:23:54,200
[SPEAKER_01] i onda mi to daje nekakvu mirnoću isto

382
00:23:54,200 --> 00:23:57,000
[SPEAKER_01] i kad sam tek taj apartman uzela,

383
00:23:57,000 --> 00:23:59,400
[SPEAKER_01] sredila i sve i dala u dnevni najam,

384
00:23:59,400 --> 00:24:01,579
[SPEAKER_01] bila mi agencija.

385
00:24:01,579 --> 00:24:02,500
[SPEAKER_01] I onda bih, ja iza ti,

386
00:24:02,500 --> 00:24:03,960
[SPEAKER_01] imali su neke čistačice,

387
00:24:03,960 --> 00:24:04,940
[SPEAKER_01] bile su Filipinke

388
00:24:04,940 --> 00:24:06,500
[SPEAKER_01] i ja sam uvijek iza njih dolazila

389
00:24:06,500 --> 00:24:07,420
[SPEAKER_01] i to provjeravala,

390
00:24:07,420 --> 00:24:09,220
[SPEAKER_01] pa onda nisam baš bila uvijek zadovoljna.

391
00:24:09,740 --> 00:24:10,539
[SPEAKER_01] I ja sam jednog dana rekla,

392
00:24:10,539 --> 00:24:12,339
[SPEAKER_01] pa sašto da maltretiram te žene,

393
00:24:12,339 --> 00:24:13,240
[SPEAKER_01] ja ću to raditi.

394
00:24:13,240 --> 00:24:14,640
[SPEAKER_01] I onda kad sam počela ja to čistiti,

395
00:24:14,640 --> 00:24:16,099
[SPEAKER_01] se rekao, ne treba mi ni agencija,

396
00:24:16,099 --> 00:24:16,920
[SPEAKER_01] ja ću to i voditi.

397
00:24:16,920 --> 00:24:19,019
[SPEAKER_01] Tako da sam preuzela sad sve to samo

398
00:24:19,019 --> 00:24:20,839
[SPEAKER_01] i već jedno sam mjeseci to sama vodim

399
00:24:20,839 --> 00:24:22,039
[SPEAKER_01] i jako sam zadovoljna

400
00:24:22,039 --> 00:24:24,140
[SPEAKER_01] i imam jako ljepe komentare,

401
00:24:24,140 --> 00:24:25,220
[SPEAKER_01] stranaca i sve

402
00:24:25,220 --> 00:24:28,220
[SPEAKER_01] i kažem, nije mi teško

403
00:24:28,220 --> 00:24:29,480
[SPEAKER_01] zasukat rukave, recimo,

404
00:24:29,480 --> 00:24:31,420
[SPEAKER_01] juče sam to baš prije,

405
00:24:31,420 --> 00:24:33,279
[SPEAKER_01] juče sam sa sastanka

406
00:24:33,279 --> 00:24:35,200
[SPEAKER_01] išla čistiti apartman četiri sata,

407
00:24:35,200 --> 00:24:36,559
[SPEAKER_01] mislim, meni je to sve normalno,

408
00:24:37,079 --> 00:24:38,440
[SPEAKER_01] a sutra opet idem, recimo,

409
00:24:38,440 --> 00:24:40,019
[SPEAKER_01] znaš, meni ti je to tak nekako

410
00:24:40,019 --> 00:24:40,859
[SPEAKER_01] ispušni ventil,

411
00:24:40,859 --> 00:24:42,519
[SPEAKER_01] ja ti upalim glazbu,

412
00:24:42,519 --> 00:24:43,720
[SPEAKER_01] zasušem rukave,

413
00:24:43,720 --> 00:24:45,500
[SPEAKER_01] imam svoju onu manduru,

414
00:24:45,500 --> 00:24:46,619
[SPEAKER_01] znaš, za čišćenje

415
00:24:46,619 --> 00:24:47,460
[SPEAKER_01] i idemo.

416
00:24:47,460 --> 00:24:50,940
[SPEAKER_01] Jednostavno, tako mi je i doma,

417
00:24:50,940 --> 00:24:52,400
[SPEAKER_01] znaš, i doma djeca su ono

418
00:24:52,400 --> 00:24:53,619
[SPEAKER_01] prilično moja,

419
00:24:53,619 --> 00:24:55,980
[SPEAKER_01] ajmo reći, naviknuta

420
00:24:55,980 --> 00:24:57,960
[SPEAKER_01] na taj nekakav maminu čistoću,

421
00:24:57,960 --> 00:24:59,359
[SPEAKER_01] tako da oni ono stvarno

422
00:24:59,359 --> 00:25:00,599
[SPEAKER_01] igračke pospreme za sebe,

423
00:25:00,599 --> 00:25:01,700
[SPEAKER_01] ja i to od malena učim

424
00:25:01,700 --> 00:25:02,599
[SPEAKER_01] i stvarno su dobri.

425
00:25:02,680 --> 00:25:03,859
[SPEAKER_01] na neško mi dođu gozi i kažu,

426
00:25:03,859 --> 00:25:05,700
[SPEAKER_01] i baš ti djeca ono poslušajte,

427
00:25:05,700 --> 00:25:06,700
[SPEAKER_01] spreme te igračke,

428
00:25:06,700 --> 00:25:08,940
[SPEAKER_01] jesu jer sam prvu godinu dana

429
00:25:08,940 --> 00:25:10,519
[SPEAKER_01] se na trepavica više popela

430
00:25:10,519 --> 00:25:11,259
[SPEAKER_01] na to posliraju,

431
00:25:11,259 --> 00:25:12,420
[SPEAKER_01] pa su se više navikli,

432
00:25:12,420 --> 00:25:13,640
[SPEAKER_01] suprug njih isto prilično,

433
00:25:13,640 --> 00:25:14,519
[SPEAKER_01] ono, znaš, pedantan,

434
00:25:14,519 --> 00:25:15,920
[SPEAKER_01] tako da smo mi jedna onako

435
00:25:15,920 --> 00:25:17,839
[SPEAKER_01] prilično pedantna obitelj doma,

436
00:25:17,839 --> 00:25:18,420
[SPEAKER_01] baš dobro.

437
00:25:18,420 --> 00:25:20,019
[SPEAKER_01] I podijelili smo se

438
00:25:20,019 --> 00:25:21,400
[SPEAKER_01] sa tim kućanskim poslovima,

439
00:25:21,400 --> 00:25:23,500
[SPEAKER_01] do duše ja više čistim,

440
00:25:23,500 --> 00:25:24,680
[SPEAKER_01] on nije baš ljubitelj čišćenja,

441
00:25:24,680 --> 00:25:25,240
[SPEAKER_01] čišćenja,

442
00:25:25,240 --> 00:25:27,240
[SPEAKER_01] ali kuhinju voli pospremiti

443
00:25:27,240 --> 00:25:28,019
[SPEAKER_01] i voli kuhat.

444
00:25:28,019 --> 00:25:30,000
[SPEAKER_01] Tako da smo ti mi ono malo se obrnuli,

445
00:25:30,000 --> 00:25:31,380
[SPEAKER_01] on ti kuha većinski,

446
00:25:31,380 --> 00:25:32,799
[SPEAKER_01] i ja nekad naravno skuham,

447
00:25:32,799 --> 00:25:34,079
[SPEAKER_01] ali uglavnom mi super kuha

448
00:25:34,079 --> 00:25:35,559
[SPEAKER_01] i odličan je u tome

449
00:25:35,559 --> 00:25:36,319
[SPEAKER_01] i svakam u čas

450
00:25:36,319 --> 00:25:38,059
[SPEAKER_01] i pospremi nakon svog kuhanja,

451
00:25:38,059 --> 00:25:39,140
[SPEAKER_01] znači super je.

452
00:25:39,140 --> 00:25:40,579
[SPEAKER_01] I on voli ono svešom,

453
00:25:40,579 --> 00:25:41,480
[SPEAKER_01] znaš, veš, talje,

454
00:25:41,480 --> 00:25:42,579
[SPEAKER_01] prat, dizati to.

455
00:25:42,579 --> 00:25:44,019
[SPEAKER_01] Ja pegla,

456
00:25:44,019 --> 00:25:45,039
[SPEAKER_01] mrzim peglanje,

457
00:25:45,039 --> 00:25:45,680
[SPEAKER_01] koga je izmislio,

458
00:25:46,359 --> 00:25:48,079
[SPEAKER_01] ali i drugo,

459
00:25:48,079 --> 00:25:49,420
[SPEAKER_01] sve ja volim ono kupone,

460
00:25:49,420 --> 00:25:50,220
[SPEAKER_01] sve, sve, sve to.

461
00:25:50,220 --> 00:25:51,779
[SPEAKER_01] Tako da nije problem,

462
00:25:51,779 --> 00:25:53,359
[SPEAKER_01] znači na djeca škola vrtić,

463
00:25:53,359 --> 00:25:55,119
[SPEAKER_01] pa ono imam i slobodnog tog vremena

464
00:25:55,119 --> 00:25:56,160
[SPEAKER_01] za to sve

465
00:25:56,160 --> 00:25:57,279
[SPEAKER_01] i nađem i vremena

466
00:25:57,279 --> 00:25:58,079
[SPEAKER_01] i za prijatelje,

467
00:25:58,079 --> 00:25:58,559
[SPEAKER_01] i za sve.

468
00:25:58,559 --> 00:26:00,519
[SPEAKER_01] Ono, posložim se,

469
00:26:00,519 --> 00:26:01,779
[SPEAKER_01] ja prilično sam onako,

470
00:26:01,779 --> 00:26:03,839
[SPEAKER_01] imam energija aktivna,

471
00:26:03,839 --> 00:26:04,660
[SPEAKER_01] sam uvijek bila

472
00:26:04,660 --> 00:26:05,279
[SPEAKER_01] i evo,

473
00:26:05,279 --> 00:26:07,160
[SPEAKER_01] ideš dan po dan

474
00:26:07,160 --> 00:26:07,619
[SPEAKER_01] i to je to.

475
00:26:07,619 --> 00:26:10,740
[SPEAKER_00] Baš mi je predobročet

476
00:26:10,740 --> 00:26:12,359
[SPEAKER_00] koliko si u svemu tam jednostavna

477
00:26:12,359 --> 00:26:14,660
[SPEAKER_00] i koliko si,

478
00:26:15,400 --> 00:26:16,880
[SPEAKER_00] onako svoja,

479
00:26:16,880 --> 00:26:18,019
[SPEAKER_00] baš svoja.

480
00:26:18,019 --> 00:26:18,740
[SPEAKER_01] Pa nije,

481
00:26:18,740 --> 00:26:20,019
[SPEAKER_01] znači nije tu sramota,

482
00:26:20,019 --> 00:26:20,880
[SPEAKER_01] sramota je

483
00:26:20,880 --> 00:26:22,099
[SPEAKER_01] ne radit ništa,

484
00:26:22,099 --> 00:26:22,460
[SPEAKER_01] ono,

485
00:26:22,460 --> 00:26:24,519
[SPEAKER_01] i očekiva da ti neko nešto plati,

486
00:26:24,519 --> 00:26:24,779
[SPEAKER_01] ono,

487
00:26:24,779 --> 00:26:25,599
[SPEAKER_01] a ništa ne radiš,

488
00:26:25,599 --> 00:26:26,099
[SPEAKER_01] šta znam,

489
00:26:26,099 --> 00:26:26,420
[SPEAKER_01] ono,

490
00:26:26,420 --> 00:26:28,200
[SPEAKER_01] ja sam jako sretna,

491
00:26:28,200 --> 00:26:28,539
[SPEAKER_01] meni kažem,

492
00:26:28,539 --> 00:26:29,440
[SPEAKER_01] možda ti baš voliš to,

493
00:26:29,440 --> 00:26:31,539
[SPEAKER_01] ja kad vidim da je to sve na svom mjestu,

494
00:26:31,539 --> 00:26:32,180
[SPEAKER_01] da sam ja ostala

495
00:26:32,180 --> 00:26:33,000
[SPEAKER_01] na one čokoladice

496
00:26:33,000 --> 00:26:34,140
[SPEAKER_01] gdje sam htjela gostima,

497
00:26:34,140 --> 00:26:35,180
[SPEAKER_01] napišem im poruku,

498
00:26:35,180 --> 00:26:35,440
[SPEAKER_01] znaš,

499
00:26:35,440 --> 00:26:36,400
[SPEAKER_01] vlastitom rukom

500
00:26:36,400 --> 00:26:37,400
[SPEAKER_01] da im se zahvalim

501
00:26:37,400 --> 00:26:37,759
